# thoth_endpoint_api_key

Issues short-lived endpoint-scoped API keys.

Organization-scoped keys are intentionally not creatable through Terraform/Pulumi.
Create organization keys with `thothctl api-keys create ...` and pass them to
the provider via `THOTH_API_KEY` or `org_api_key`.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_endpoint_api_key" "endpoint_exec" {
  name            = "endpoint-exec"
  scope_target_id = "endpoint-123"
  permissions     = ["execute", "read"]
  ttl_seconds     = 1800
  jit_reason      = "endpoint-remediation"
}
```
